  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, there are several good options for camera phones under \u20b910,000 in India. Here are a few that are often recommended for their camera performance:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo 30A**: This phone offers a 13MP dual rear camera setup, which performs well in good lighting conditions. The software optimization also helps in producing decent images.\n\n2. **Redmi 9 Prime**: Equipped with a 13MP quad-camera setup, the Redmi 9 Prime offers versatile photography options including ultra-wide, macro, and depth sensors.\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M12**: Featuring a 48MP quad-camera system, the Galaxy M12 is known for its good camera performance in this price segment, especially in daylight.\n\n4. **Poco M2**: The Poco M2 comes with a 13MP quad-camera setup and provides good image quality, suitable for casual photography needs.\n\n5. **Infinix Hot 10S**: With a 48MP primary camera, the Infinix Hot 10S offers impressive camera performance for its price, especially in well-lit conditions.\n\nRemember that camera performance can also depend on factors like software optimization and additional features. It's always a good idea to check out reviews and sample images to see which camera phone meets your expectations before making a purchase.",
